<p><span class="vocab">私<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>私</rb><rt>わたくし</rt></ruby>&nbsp;I; me</span></span>は<span class="vocab">母<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>母</rb><rt>はは</rt></ruby>&nbsp;mother</span></span>を<span class="vocab">蔭<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>蔭</rb><rt>かげ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;aside; off to the side</span></span>へ<span class="vocab">呼んで<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>呼</rb><rt>よ</rt></ruby>んで&nbsp;called; beckoned</span></span><span class="vocab">父<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>父</rb><rt>ちち</rt></ruby>&nbsp;father</span></span>の<span class="vocab">病状<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>病状</rb><rt>びょうじょう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;condition (of one's health)</span></span>を<span class="vocab">尋ねた<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>尋</rb><rt>たず</rt></ruby>ねた&nbsp;asked; inquired (about)</span></span>。</p>

